Dom Cobb (Leonardo DiCaprio) is a skilled thief, absolutely the best in the dangerous art of extraction, stealing valuable secrets from the bottom of the subconscious during the dream state, when the mind is more vulnerable. Cobb's uncanny ability makes him a coveted player in this new world of espionage new face, yet also make him an international fugitive, which will cost you everything you love.

Now offers a chance to redeem Cobb. A final work that could restore his life only if it can achieve the impossible - the creation. Instead of the perfect robbery, Cobb and his team of experts must make do the reverse: his task will not be stealing an idea, but implementing one. If they succeed, this could be the perfect crime.

But no careful planning or experience can prepare this team to face the most dangerous enemy that seems to predict each of their movements. An enemy that Cobb could just see it coming. This summer, your mind is the scene of the crime.
